inks out loud while looking for you<br></li><li>Find puzzle pieces and then solve a sliding puzzle to reveal a secret passage<br></li><li>Unscrew vent panels and crawl through them to reach new areas<br></li><li>Find keys or ways around locked doors to unlock them<br></li><li>Crouch to hide behind objects and move around silently<br></li><li>Memes<br></li><li>The game offers to save your progress when quitting the game</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292910/extras/996f75f0827aee4bb1e738db5cba0bcf.poster.avif?t=1693080390\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292910/extras/996f75f0827aee4bb1e738db5cba0bcf.webm?t=1693080390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292910/extras/996f75f0827aee4bb1e738db5cba0bcf.mp4?t=1693080390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
